These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, sunflower
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, aristoff
1. the siglo-smoker is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
2. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Flower          | sunflower | iris    |
| Sport         | volleyball   | tennis |
| Cigar   | siglo  | aristoff      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, purple
There are 2 different nationalities: german, malaysian
House: cottage, colonial
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the german##5
3. the malaysian is not to the right of the german##8
4. the cottage house is not the person who likes purple##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Color       | lilac         | purple |
| Nationality         | malaysian | german   |
| House   | cottage               | colonial  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, thriller
House: gothic-revival, futuristic
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, manager
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, garlic
1. the bartender is in an odd position##4
2. the manager is not to the right of the person eating garlic##8
3. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| House   | gothic-revival       | futuristic    |
| Job   | bartender | manager |
| Food           | asparagus        | garlic   |

