.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, traveling
2 different games are played: canasta, chess
2 different pets are kept: mouse, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | video-games | traveling |
| Game   | chess    | canasta     |
| Pet         | mouse  | cat    |
| Transport     | scooter     | boat       |

